race.description: Cowra Lamb Cowra Japan Cup Handicap
race.comment: ZALE (10) deep into the prep and racing in career best form. Took control from the low gate when a fighting head winner over 1280m at Orange. Doesn't get the same map favours here but racing too well to dismiss. HELLINDA (6) improved sharply in weaker company when he shouldered the 59.5kg to get the job done over 1200m at Corowa. Finds a deeper field this time but expected to go close. BLITZAR (3) was a month between runs when a fading eighth over 1200m at Wagga from the outside gate. Better than that and assess on the win at Hay two-runs ago. Respect from the gate. SHADDAP (15) hit the line nicely first-up without much luck and is a second-up winner in the past. Can be in the finish.
